---
title: Chermoula Yoghurt Chicken Tacos with Pickled Cucumber & Dill-Parsley Mayo
description: Few things look as colourful as these tacos — with the much loved spiced chicken inside no less! The real star of this dish is the dill and parsley-flecked mayo. There’s a herby hint amidst the expected creaminess of mayonnaise that works perfectly with each element in tonight's dish and also means you’re in for a burst of flavour.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/64f9cc366628abb5190efeb1-e0efffd8.jpeg
